  "title": "<div><br></div>",
  "content": "<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📜</font> If a student with high XP transfers power, it must come with a consequence.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> XP Transfers Are Allowed, But Come with a “Karmic Shift.”</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> If a high-XP player gives away XP, they permanently change their alignment.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> The recipient gains XP but receives a debuff (a more difficult final challenge).</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📜</font> Example: The XP Abdication Choices</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><object><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; direction: ltr\">\n<tbody>\n<tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Transfer Type</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>XP Leader’s Fate</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Recipient’s Fate</div>",
